product_name: IT CosmeticsSuperhero Elastic Stretch Volumizing & Lengthening Mascara
summary: SummaryIT Cosmetics Superhero Elastic Stretch Volumizing & Lengthening Mascara has a buildable formula that defines, curls, separates, lifts and volumizes lashes.
details: DetailsBenefitsGive your lashes superhero powers with this game-changing mascara that's clinically tested to give lashes super volume, super length and super elastic stretch in just one coat!Developed with plastic surgeons, IT Cosmetics Superhero Elastic Stretch Volumizing & Lengthening Mascara thickens and separates eyelashes to create the look of longer lashes and a full lash lineExclusive Elastic Stretch Technology lengthens and volumizes lashesLash-Changing Power Brush has a lash lift effect and helps to curl lashesSuper-buildable volumizing mascara formula thickens both long lashes and short lashesSuper black pigment contains collagen, biotin and peptides to condition as you coatOphthalmologist tested, suitable for contact wearers and ideal for sensitive eyesKey IngredientsElastic Stretch TechnologyLash-Lifting PolymersCollagenProteinsPeptidesBiotinResearch Results100% saw a fuller lash line!96% said lashes looked stretched!96% saw dramatic volume & length!96% saw plumper-looking lashes!Item 2298659How To UseStarting at the base of your lashes, wiggle brush and sweep up and through to the tips. Apply additional coats for more dramatic results, and watch your lashes transform!Beauty Tip: Want even more volume? Add additional coats! Superhero is clinically shown to give you 5x more volume after just one coat, and 14x more volume after two.IngredientsAqua (Water, Eau), Cera Carnauba / Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax / Cire De Carnauba, Cyclopentasiloxane, Oryza Sativa Cera /Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Wax, Hydrogenated Olive Oil Stearyl Esters, Alcohol Denat., Palmitic Acid, Stearic Acid, Triethanolamine, Acacia Senegal Gum, Candelilla Cera / Euphorbia Cerifera (Candelilla) Wax / Cire De Candelilla, Propylene Glycol, Phenoxyethanol, VP / VA Copolymer, Aminomethyl Propanediol, Polyvinyl Alcohol, Chlorphenesin, Ethylhexylglycerin, Glycerin, Ascorbic Acid, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Biotin, Equisetum Arvense Extract, Hydrolyzed Collagen, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil, Persea Gratissima Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate, Panthenol, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Serenoa Serrulata Fruit Extract, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Biotinoyl Tripeptide - 1, Iron Oxide (CI 77499).Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Starting at the base of your lashes, wiggle brush and sweep up and through to the tips. Apply additional coats for more dramatic results, and watch your lashes transform!Beauty Tip: Want even more volume? Add additional coats! Superhero is clinically shown to give you 5x more volume after just one coat, and 14x more volume after two.

reviews.headline: I can't get enough of this mascara
reviews.comments:
I've always been a drugstore mascara girl, I think many of them are really good. But this is so worth the splurge and I try to get it when it's on sale. 

It makes my lashes look SO long and they hold their curl all day. My biggest problem with mascaras is they look good for about an hour and then they fall flat, but this doesn't do that. Also, looks great immediately after opening, you don't have to dry it out for a few days. Can't recommend enough!

reviews.headline: Not likely
reviews.comments: It's okay but there are better mascaras for the same price.

reviews.headline: I love it!
reviews.comments: Best mascara I have ever used.  A bit pricey butâ€¦.. I have trouble with eye makeup causing irritation but this product does not.  I will buy this product again when it goes on sale again.  I probably won't order off the website though because I don't always receive my entire order.

reviews.comments: I live this mascara, it's magic

reviews.headline: Not what it used to be
reviews.comments: I have been a long time fan of this mascara. However, the last tube I purchased performs significantly less than previous tubes. It flakes so much it's half off by the end of the day. My eyes are irritated from the flakes getting into my eyes all day. It also weighs my lashes down now. I'm so disappointed.

reviews.headline: I would definitely buy again
reviews.comments: I wasnt sure if i would like this product especially bc its a lil pricey however i was pleasantly surprised how good it worked my eye lashes looked great after using this mascara.

reviews.headline: Too flakey
reviews.comments: This mascara did not work for me! Gets all over eyelids and flakey!

reviews.headline: Best I have ever used.
reviews.comments: Only use this one particular It mascara.

reviews.headline: Whew!
reviews.comments: This is the perfect mascara! I generally go for tubing because it gives a better extension, however, this mascara gives CRAZY lift and length! Best of all, no clumping even with two coats. It's my new favorite!

reviews.headline: The best BASE for fullness
reviews.comments: I love using this before I use another voluminous mascara over it. Give it perfect fullness/base. Only thing I don't like- the applicator gets mucked up quicker than I would like. So, because of that I gave it a three. Fix the applicator or the price.

reviews.headline: Clumpy Clump Clump Clump
reviews.comments: When I first started using this mascara it seemed to be great but about a month in it turned EXTREMELY clumpy. So frustrating. Already looking for a different mascara.

reviews.headline: FLAKY AND SMUDGE
reviews.comments: I really tried to like this mascara but after 3rd time of using it I gave UP.  It's FLAKY, CLUMPY, and smudgy. I wouldn't buy again.

reviews.headline: Best Mascara
reviews.comments: Really is the best mascara.  Last so long and applies smoothly.

reviews.headline: Best Mascara!
reviews.comments: I get seriouse eye reactions and swelling when using basic brand mascaras. I finally found this one and haven't got a reaction since! It creates super long lashes and i love the volume!

reviews.headline: My second time buying
reviews.comments: This is my new favorite. Goes on so easily. Separates and makes my lashes look incredible. Also easy to come off.

reviews.headline: My favorite mascara!
reviews.comments: I always go back to this mascara

reviews.headline: My favorite mascara of all time
reviews.comments: I have nothing but good things to say about this mascara.  I have always had very unnoticeable eyelashes, but one I apply this mascara my lashes look amazing! It makes my lashes long and beautiful, and also makes my eyes pop.  I will buy again.

reviews.headline: Favorite mascara
reviews.comments: This is by far my favorite mascara, but if you don't like a little clumpy, you're not gonna like it.

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again
reviews.comments: nice and thick, adds body and length
